- We already look the part. - Exactly.

538
00:19:58,840 --> 00:19:59,900
That makes sense.

539
00:19:59,900 --> 00:20:01,810
I fully understand Hyeong Seon's intentions.

540
00:20:03,510 --> 00:20:05,710
Haha, no way.

541
00:20:05,710 --> 00:20:07,010
- My gosh. - Velvet Dress Ok Jung.

542
