546
00:20:16,820 --> 00:20:18,390
You're the spitting image of her.

547
00:20:18,920 --> 00:20:20,620
Have you seen Jae Seok's mom before?

548
00:20:21,890 --> 00:20:23,030
He looks exactly like her.

549
00:20:23,590 --> 00:20:25,130
- Same with my mom. - Is Jae Seok...

550
00:20:25,130 --> 00:20:27,500
a special kind of squid? He's getting accessories.

551
00:20:28,270 --> 00:20:30,370
Jae Seok looks like a prince.

552
00:20:30,370 --> 00:20:31,600
- Right? - Yes.

553
00:20:31,800 --> 00:20:34,400
As a minion, I didn't get any embellishments.

554
00:20:34,400 --> 00:20:35,440
You're my servant, after all.

555
00:20:36,440 --> 00:20:37,670
A servant should stay invisible.

556
00:20:38,580 --> 00:20:41,110
Stop acting like a prince when you're just a baby octopus.

557
00:20:41,110 --> 00:20:43,250
He's still a baby octopus prince. Have some respect.

558
00:20:43,250 --> 00:20:44,580
Those Antenna goons.

559
00:20:44,580 --> 00:20:45,820
- Seriously? - What?

560
00:20:45,820 --> 00:20:47,150
Why would you bring up our agency?

561
00:20:47,150 --> 00:20:48,220
Every single time...

562
00:20:48,220 --> 00:20:49,650
Why would you bring up our agency?

563
00:20:49,650 --> 00:20:50,720
Why would you bring that up?

564
00:20:50,720 --> 00:20:52,020
