565
00:20:52,020 --> 00:20:54,190
You're just a baby octopus, so stop saying you're a prince.

566
00:20:54,190 --> 00:20:55,760
- Jae Seok's a prince. Look. - Thank you.

567
00:20:55,760 --> 00:20:57,330
His outfit's nothing like mine.

568
