572
00:21:06,570 --> 00:21:08,570
I'll be in a regal costume today.

573
00:21:09,210 --> 00:21:11,440
Of course. Jae Seok won the race, didn't he?

574
00:21:11,910 --> 00:21:12,910
What's that?

575
00:21:13,280 --> 00:21:14,410
That's for the prince's servant.

576
00:21:14,540 --> 00:21:16,210
Unbelievable.

577
00:21:16,850 --> 00:21:19,850
