578
00:21:20,080 --> 00:21:22,420
- There. - Hold on. This is a bit annoying.

579
00:21:22,520 --> 00:21:25,160
Jae Seok, they gave me a tin to carry around.

580
00:21:25,160 --> 00:21:26,190
That's just how it is.

581
00:21:26,190 --> 00:21:27,190
- Hold on. - Really?

582
00:21:27,190 --> 00:21:29,560
Why do you both look like you have makeup on?

583
00:21:30,060 --> 00:21:32,230
Isn't it funny to see him act regal in that costume?

584
00:21:32,530 --> 00:21:33,730
He's trying to act like a prince.

585
00:21:36,130 --> 00:21:38,370
What time's the show?

586
00:21:39,970 --> 00:21:41,070
Is this the green room?

587
00:21:41,070 --> 00:21:42,140
When do you go on stage, ma'am?

588
00:21:42,770 --> 00:21:44,040
Mr. Baby Octopus.

589
00:21:44,270 --> 00:21:46,010
Mr. Baby Octopus, are you coming from your show?

590
00:21:46,010 --> 00:21:47,080
- Are you done? - Yes.

591
00:21:47,080 --> 00:21:48,210
- Were you marching? - I wrapped up a session.

592
00:21:48,210 --> 00:21:49,210
Which time slot was that?

593
00:21:49,210 --> 00:21:51,010
I go back on at 11am.

594
00:21:52,720 --> 00:21:55,390
Feel free to use this table.

595
00:21:56,090 --> 00:21:58,960
- Sure. - He always carries around a table.

596
