Get lucky this year.

598
00:22:04,860 --> 00:22:06,460
- Please head downstairs. - It must be a group shot.

599
00:22:06,460 --> 00:22:07,860
- Do we all go downstairs? - It's a group shot!

600
00:22:07,860 --> 00:22:09,900
Are you promoting an orthopedic clinic?

601
00:22:10,300 --> 00:22:11,940
