602
00:22:11,940 --> 00:22:13,140
- It's a dentist. - A clinic for arthritis.

603
00:22:13,140 --> 00:22:14,870
- Right. - No, a dental clinic.

604
00:22:15,470 --> 00:22:16,670
Isn't it funny that he dressed up as a baby octopus...

605
00:22:16,670 --> 00:22:17,870
even though he won?

606
